or: #F7F7F7; border: 1px #F0F0F0 solid; padding:0px 4px 0px 4px\" class=\"hierarchy\"><a href=\"https://hl7.org/fhir/R4/codesystem-item-type.html#item-type-choice\">choice</a></td><td style=\"vertical-align: top; text-align : var(--ig-left,left); background-color: #F7F7F7; border: 1px #F0F0F0 solid; padding:0px 4px 0px 4px\" class=\"hierarchy\">Value Set: <a href=\"ValueSet-QIMMZD13_IMMZ.D.DE126.html\">IMMZ.D.DE126 ValueSet for Disease targeted</a></td></tr>#xD;\n<tr style=\"border: 1px #F0F0F0 solid; padding:0px; vertical-align: top; background-color: white\"><td style=\"vertical-align: top; text-align : var(--ig-left,left); background-color: white; border: 1px #F0F0F0 solid; padding:0px 4px 0px 4px; white-space: nowrap; background-image: url(tbl_bck00.png)\" id=\"item.dueDateOfNextDose\" class=\"hierarchy\"><img src=\"tbl_spacer.png\" alt=\".\" style=\"background-color: inherit\" class=\"hierarchy\"/><img src=\"tbl_vjoin_end.png\" alt=\".\" style=\"background-color: inherit\" class=\"hierarchy\"/><img src=\"icon-q-date.png\" alt=\".\" style=\"background-color: white; background-color: inherit\" title=\"date\" class=\"hierarchy\"/> dueDateOfNextDose</td><td style=\"vertical-align: top; text-align : var(--ig-left,left); background-color: white; border: 1px #F0F0F0 solid; padding:0px 4px 0px 4px\" class=\"hierarchy\">Due date of next dose</td><td style=\"vertical-align: top; text-align : var(--ig-left,left); background-color: white; border: 1px #F0F0F0 solid; padding:0px 4px 0px 4px\" class=\"hierarchy\">0..1</td><td style=\"vertical-align: top; text-align : var(--ig-left,left); background-color: white; border: 1px #F0F0F0 solid; padding:0px 4px 0px 4px\" class=\"hierarchy\"><a href=\"https://hl7.org/fhir/R4/codesystem-item-type.html#item-type-date\">date</a></td><td style=\"vertical-align: top; text-align : var(--ig-left,left); background-color: white; border: 1px #F0F0F0 solid; padding:0px 4px 0px 4px\" class=\"hierarchy\"/></tr>#xD;\n<tr><td colspan=\"5\" class=\"hierarchy\"><br/><a href=\"https://hl7.org/fhir/R4/formats.html#table\" title=\"Legend for this format\"><img src=\"data:image/png;base64,\" alt=\"doco\" style=\"background-color: inherit\"/> Documentation for this format</a></td></tr></table><h2>Contained Resources</h2><hr/><p class=\"res-header-id\"><b>ValueSet #IMMZ.D.DE258</b></p><a name=\"QIMMZD13/IMMZ.D.DE258\"> </a><a name=\"hcQIMMZD13/IMMZ.D.DE258\"> </a><p>This value set expansion contains 4 concepts.</p><table class=\"codes\"><tr><td><b>System</b></td><td style=\"white-space:nowrap\"><b>Code</b></td><td><b>Display</b></td><td><b>Definition</b></td></tr><tr><td><a name=\"QIMMZD13/IMMZ.D.DE258-http://smart.who.int/immunizations/CodeSystem/IMMZ.D-DE259\"> </a><code>http://smart.who.int/immunizations/CodeSystem/IMMZ.D</code></td><td style=\"white-space:nowrap\">  <a href=\"CodeSystem-IMMZ.D.html#IMMZ.D-DE259\">DE259</a></td><td>Primary series</td><td>Indicates that the client received the primary vaccination series of a product/antigen. This is also applicable for antigens with one dose</td></tr><tr><td><a name=\"QIMMZD13/IMMZ.D.DE258-http://smart.who.int/immunizations/CodeSystem/IMMZ.D-DE260\"> </a><code>http://smart.who.int/immunizations/CodeSystem/IMMZ.D</code></td><td style=\"white-space:nowrap\">  <a href=\"CodeSystem-IMMZ.D.html#IMMZ.D-DE260\">DE260</a></td><td>Dose 0</td><td>Indicates that the client received a dose of a product/ antigen that is not a part of the primary vaccination series and is administered before the primary vaccination series is provided</td></tr><tr><td><a name=\"QIMMZD13/IMMZ.D.DE258-http://smart.who.int/immunizations/CodeSystem/IMMZ.D-DE261\"> </a><code>http://smart.who.int/immunizations/CodeSystem/IMMZ.D</code></td><td style=\"white-space:nowrap\">  <a href=\"CodeSystem-IMMZ.D.html#IMMZ.D-DE261\">DE261</a></td><td>Supplementary dose</td><td>Indicates that the client received a supplementary dose of a product/antigen</td></tr><tr><td><a name=\"QIMMZD13/IMMZ.D.DE258-http://smart.who.int/immunizations/CodeSystem/IMMZ.D-DE262\"> </a><code>http://smart.who.int/immunizations/CodeSystem/IMMZ.D</code></td><td style=\"white-space:nowrap\">  <a href=\"CodeSystem-IMMZ.D.html#IMMZ.D-DE262\">DE262</a></td><td>Booster dose</td><td>Indicates that the client received booster dose of a product/antigen</td></tr></table><hr/><p class=\"res-header-id\"><b>ValueSet #IMMZ.D.DE204</b></p><a name=\"QIMMZD13/IMMZ.D.DE204\"> </a><a name=\"hcQIMMZD13/IMMZ.D.DE204\"> </a><p>This value set expansion contains 3 concepts.</p><table class=\"codes\"><tr><td><b>System</b></td><td style=\"white-space:nowrap\"><b>Code</b></td><td><b>Display</b></td><td><b>Definition</b></td></tr><tr><td><a name=\"QIMMZD13/IMMZ.D.DE204-http://smart.who.int/immunizations/CodeSystem/IMMZ.D-DE205\"> </a><code>http://smart.who.int/immunizations/CodeSystem/IMMZ.D</code></td><td style=\"white-space:nowrap\">  <a href=\"CodeSystem-IMMZ.D.html#IMMZ.D-DE205\">DE205</a></td><td>HIV-positive</td><td>The client is known to be HIV-positive</td></tr><tr><td><a name=\"QIMMZD13/IMMZ.D.DE204-http://smart.who.int/immunizations/CodeSystem/IMMZ.D-DE206\"> </a><code>http://smart.who.int/immunizations/CodeSystem/IMMZ.D</code></td><td style=\"white-space:nowrap\">  <a href=\"CodeSystem-IMMZ.D.html#IMMZ.D-DE206\">DE206</a></td><td>HIV-negative</td><td>The client is known to be HIV-negative</td></tr><tr><td><a name=\"QIMMZD13/IMMZ.D.DE204-http://smart.who.int/immunizations/CodeSystem/IMMZ.D-DE207\"> </a><code>http://smart.who.int/immunizations/CodeSystem/IMMZ.D</code></td><td style=\"white-space:nowrap\">  <a href=\"CodeSystem-IMMZ.D.html#IMMZ.D-DE207\">DE207</a></td><td>Unknown</td><td>The client's HIV status is unknown</td></tr></table><hr/><p class=\"res-header-id\"><b>ValueSet #IMMZ.D.DE212</b></p><a name=\"QIMMZD13/IMMZ.D.DE212\"> </a><a name=\"hcQIMMZD13/IMMZ.D.DE212\"> </a><p>This value set expansion contains 2 concepts.</p><table class=\"codes\"><tr><td><b>System</b></td><td style=\"white-space:nowrap\"><b>Code</b></td><td><b>Display</b></td><td><b>Definition</b></td></tr><tr><td><a name=\"QIMMZD13/IMMZ.D.DE212-http://smart.who.int/immunizations/CodeSystem/IMMZ.D-DE213\"> </a><code>http://smart.who.int/immunizations/CodeSystem/IMMZ.D</code></td><td style=\"white-space:nowrap\">  <a href=\"CodeSystem-IMMZ.D.html#IMMZ.D-DE213\">DE213</a></td><td>IPV</td><td>Inactivated polio vaccine (IPV)</td></tr><tr><td><a name=\"QIMMZD13/IMMZ.D.DE212-http://smart.who.int/immunizations/CodeSystem/IMMZ.D-DE214\"> </a><code>http://smart.who.int/immunizations/CodeSystem/IMMZ.D</code></td><td style=\"white-space:nowrap\">  <a href=\"CodeSystem-IMMZ.D.html#IMMZ.D-DE214\">DE214</a></td><td>bOPV</td><td>Bivalent oral polio vaccine (bOPV)</td></tr></table><hr/><p class=\"res-header-id\"><b>ValueSet #IMMZ.D.DE216</b></p><a name=\"QIMMZD13/IMMZ.D.DE216\"> </a><a name=\"hcQIMMZD13/IMMZ.D.DE216\"> </a><p>This value set expansion contains 3 concepts.</p><table class=\"codes\"><tr><td><b>System</b></td><td style=\"white-space:nowrap\"><b>Code</b></td><td><b>Display</b></td><td><b>Definition</b></td></tr><tr><td><a name=\"QIMMZD13/IMMZ.D.DE216-http://smart.who.int/immunizations/CodeSystem/IMMZ.D-DE217\"> </a><code>http://smart.who.int/immunizations/CodeSystem/IMMZ.D</code></td><td style=\"white-space:nowrap\">  <a href=\"CodeSystem-IMMZ.D.html#IMMZ.D-DE217\">DE217</a></td><td>Inactivated Vero cell-derived vaccine</td><td>Inactivated Vero cell-derived JE vaccine type</td></tr><tr><td><a name=\"QIMMZD13/IMMZ.D.DE216-http://smart.who.int/immunizations/CodeSystem/IMMZ.D-DE218\"> </a><code>http://smart.who.int/immunizations/CodeSystem/IMMZ.D</code></td><td style=\"white-space:nowrap\">  <a href=\"CodeSystem-IMMZ.D.html#IMMZ.D-DE218\">DE218</a></td><td>Live attenuated vaccine</td><td>Live attenuated JE vaccine type</td></tr><tr><td><a name=\"QIMMZD13/IMMZ.D.DE216-http://smart.who.int/immunizations/CodeSystem/IMMZ.D-DE219\"> </a><code>http://smart.who.int/immunizations/CodeSystem/IMMZ.D</code></td><td style=\"white-space:nowrap\">  <a href=\"CodeSystem-IMMZ.D.html#IMMZ.D-DE219\">DE219</a></td><td>Live recombinant vaccine</td><td>Live recombinant JE vaccine type</td></tr></table><hr/><p class=\"res-header-id\"><b>ValueSet #IMMZ.D.DE220</b></p><a name=\"QIMMZD13/IMMZ.D.DE220\"> </a><a name=\"hcQIMMZD13/IMMZ.D.DE220\"> </a><p>This value set expansion contains 4 concepts.</p><table class=\"codes\"><tr><td><b>System</b></td><td style=\"white-space:nowrap\"><b>Code</b></td><td><b>Display</b></td><td><b>Definition</b></td></tr><tr><td><a name=\"QIMMZD13/IMMZ.D.DE220-http://smart.who.int/immunizations/CodeSystem/IMMZ.D-DE221\"> </a><code>http://smart.who.int/immunizations/CodeSystem/IMMZ.D</code></td><td style=\"white-space:nowrap\">  <a href=\"CodeSystem-IMMZ.D.html#IMMZ.D-DE221\">DE221</a></td><td>FSME-Immun</td><td>FSME-Immun vaccine product, which is an inactivated whole-virus vaccine for TBE</td></tr><tr><td><a name=\"QIMMZD13/IMMZ.D.DE220-http://smart.who.int/immunizations/CodeSystem/IMMZ.D-DE222\"> </a><code>http://smart.who.int/immunizations/CodeSystem/IMMZ.D</code></td><td style=\"white-space:nowrap\">  <a href=\"CodeSystem-IMMZ.D.html#IMMZ.D-DE222\">DE222</a></td><td>Encepur</td><td>Encepur vaccine product, which is an inactivated viral vaccine for TBE</td></tr><tr><td><a name=\"QIMMZD13/IMMZ.D.DE220-http://smart.who.int/immunizations/CodeSystem/IMMZ.D-DE223\"> </a><code>http://smart.who.int/immunizations/CodeSystem/IMMZ.D</code></td><td style=\"white-space:nowrap\">  <a href=\"CodeSystem-IMMZ.D.html#IMMZ.D-DE223\">DE223</a></td><td>TBE-Moscow</td><td>TBE-Moscow vaccine product, which is a vaccine for TBE</td></tr><tr><td><a name=\"QIMMZD13/IMMZ.D.DE220-http://smart.who.int/immunizations/CodeSystem/IMMZ.D-DE224\"> </a><code>http://smart.who.int/immunizations/CodeSystem/IMMZ.D</code></td><td style=\"white-space:nowrap\">  <a href=\"CodeSystem-IMMZ.D.html#IMMZ.D-DE224\">DE224</a></td><td>EnceVir</td><td>EnceVir vaccine product, which is a vaccine for TBE</td></tr></table><hr/><p class=\"res-header-id\"><b>ValueSet #IMMZ.D.DE225</b></p><a name=\"QIMMZD13/IMMZ.D.DE225\"> </a><a name=\"hcQIMMZD13/IMMZ.D.DE225\"> </a><p>This value set expansion contains 3 concepts.</p><table class=\"codes\"><tr><td><b>System</b></td><td style=\"white-space:nowrap\"><b>Code</b></td><td><b>Display</b></td><td><b>Definition</b></td></tr><tr><td><a name=\"QIMMZD13/IMMZ.D.DE225-http://smart.who.int/immunizations/CodeSystem/IMMZ.D-DE226\"> </a><code>http://smart.who.int/immunizations/CodeSystem/IMMZ.D</code></td><td style=\"white-space:nowrap\">  <a href=\"CodeSystem-IMMZ.D.html#IMMZ.D-DE226\">DE226</a></td><td>Typbar-TCV</td><td>Typbar typhoid conjugate vaccine (Typbar-TCV)</td></tr><tr><td><a name=\"QIMMZD13/IMMZ.D.DE225-http://smart.who.int/immunizations/CodeSystem/IMMZ.D-DE227\"> </a><code>http://smart.who.int/immunizations/CodeSystem/IMMZ.D</code></td><td style=\"white-space:nowrap\">  <a href=\"CodeSystem-IMMZ.D.html#IMMZ.D-DE227\">DE227</a></td><td>ViPS</td><td>Vi polysaccharide (ViPS) vaccine</td></tr><tr><td><a name=\"QIMMZD13/IMMZ.D.DE225-http://smart.who.int/immunizations/CodeSystem/IMMZ.D-DE228\"> </a><code>http://smart.who.int/immunizations/CodeSystem/IMMZ.D</code></td><td style=\"white-space:nowrap\">  <a href=\"CodeSystem-IMMZ.D.html#IMMZ.D-DE228\">DE228</a></td><td>Ty21a</td><td>Ty21a vaccine</td></tr></table><hr/><p class=\"res-header-id\"><b>ValueSet #IMMZ.D.DE229</b></p><a name=\"QIMMZD13/IMMZ.D.DE229\"> </a><a name=\"hcQIMMZD13/IMMZ.D.DE229\"> </a><p>This value set expansion contains 2 concepts.</p><table class=\"codes\"><tr><td><b>System</b></td><td style=\"white-space:nowrap\"><b>Code</b></td><td><b>Display</b></td><td><b>Definition</b></td></tr><tr><td><a name=\"QIMMZD13/IMMZ.D.DE229-http://smart.who.int/immunizations/CodeSystem/IMMZ.D-DE230\"> </a><code>http://smart.who.int/immunizations/CodeSystem/IMMZ.D</code></td><td style=\"white-space:nowrap\">  <a href=\"CodeSystem-IMMZ.D.html#IMMZ.D-DE230\">DE230</a></td><td>WC vaccine</td><td>Killed whole-cell (WC) only cholera vaccine</td></tr><tr><td><a name=\"QIMMZD13/IMMZ.D.DE229-http://smart.who.int/immunizations/CodeSystem/IMMZ.D-DE231\"> </a><code>http://smart.who.int/immunizations/CodeSystem/IMMZ.D</code></td><td style=\"white-space:nowrap\">  <a href=\"CodeSystem-IMMZ.D.html#IMMZ.D-DE231\">DE231</a></td><td>WC-rBS vaccine</td><td>Vaccine contains a mixture of the recombinant B subunit (rBS) of cholera toxin plus killed WC</td></tr></table><hr/><p class=\"res-header-id\"><b>ValueSet #IMMZ.D.DE232</b></p><a name=\"QIMMZD13/IMMZ.D.DE232\"> </a><a name=\"hcQIMMZD13/IMMZ.D.DE232\"> </a><p>This value set expansion contains 4 concepts.</p><table class=\"codes\"><tr><td><b>System</b></td><td style=\"white-space:nowrap\"><b>Code</b></td><td><b>Display</b></td><td><b>Definition</b></td></tr><tr><td><a name=\"QIMMZD13/IMMZ.D.DE232-http://smart.who.int/immunizations/CodeSystem/IMMZ.D-DE233\"> </a><code>http://smart.who.int/immunizations/CodeSystem/IMMZ.D</code></td><td style=\"white-space:nowrap\">  <a href=\"CodeSystem-IMMZ.D.html#IMMZ.D-DE233\">DE233</a></td><td>MenA conjugate vaccine (5µg)</td><td>Monovalent serogroup A (MenA) conjugate vaccine (5µg)</td></tr><tr><td><a name=\"QIMMZD13/IMMZ.D.DE232-http://smart.who.int/immunizations/CodeSystem/IMMZ.D-DE234\"> </a><code>http://smart.who.int/immunizations/CodeSystem/IMMZ.D</code></td><td style=\"white-space:nowrap\">  <a href=\"CodeSystem-IMMZ.D.html#IMMZ.D-DE234\">DE234</a></td><td>Monovalent MenC conjugate</td><td>Monovalent MenC conjugate vaccine</td></tr><tr><td><a name=\"QIMMZD13/IMMZ.D.DE232-http://smart.who.int/immunizations/CodeSystem/IMMZ.D-DE235\"> </a><code>http://smart.who.int/immunizations/CodeSystem/IMMZ.D</code></td><td style=\"white-space:nowrap\">  <a href=\"CodeSystem-IMMZ.D.html#IMMZ.D-DE235\">DE235</a></td><td>Quadrivalent conjugate</td><td>Quadrivalent conjugate (A,C,W135,Y-D and A,C,W135,Y-CRM) vaccines</td></tr><tr><td><a name=\"QIMMZD13/IMMZ.D.DE232-http://smart.who.int/immunizati